  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You blitz toward an enemy with feline ferocity. Make a single melee taijutsu attack, dealing your unarmed damage + 6d6 bludgeoning damage against the target on a hit.</p><p> This jutsu gains a +1 bonus to its attack roll and an extra d6 damage die for every 10 feet traveled in the target's direction this turn before making the Taijutsu attack (to a max of 60 feet).</p><p>On a hit, the target also must make a Constitution saving throw or become Dazed for 1 minute. While Dazed this way, it cannot speak, only suttering and sluring its words in cat-like meows. </p><p>If this jutsu is used as a <strong>Finisher</strong>, the target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failure, it becomes Dazed for 1 minute, and cannot move, and is incapacitated until the end of its next turn.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and any d6 damage rolled from this jutsu increases its damage die size by 1.</p>",
